name: Drippy 13
description:
Drippy Series

Drippy 13
Pigment transfer on Rives Light Weight Paper

2012

18" x 24"

Drippy 13 is a pigment transfer by Christina Gontzes. 
This process transfers the pigment from a photocopy to another surface with acrylic paint. The paper also, goes through a staining process leaving certain areas distressed and eroded. These slight abrasions give the paper a unique and worn feel.

The print is signed, titled, and dated on the back.

The print is safely packaged and shipped in a cardboard mailer tube. Shipping costs are included for orders in the United States. For international shipment, $5 shipping for the first print and free shipping for any additional prints.
